<I c="Tutorial" i="tutorial" m="tutorials.tutorial" n="tutorial_Beginner_LiveMode_Aspirations" s="314256">
  <T n="name">0xF430FEEB<!--String: "Aspirations"--></T>
  <L n="slides">
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Beginner\Beginner_Aspirations_1.png">2f7d0004:00000000:368df5a3db615171</T>
      <T n="text">0x536A889B<!--String: "A Sim’s <b><font color='#199C2C'>Aspiration</font></b> is what they aspire to be, do, and experience! In <b><font color='#199C2C'>Live Mode</font></b>, this is represented by the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Aspiration Goals</font></b> in the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Aspiration panel</font></b>. These can help you set the course of your Sim’s life!"--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Beginner\Beginner_Aspirations_2.png">2f7d0004:00000000:368df5a3db615172</T>
      <T n="text">0x821A6E5A<!--String: "Hover the cursor over each <b><font color='#199C2C'>Goal</font></b> for more information. As your Sim completes these Goals, they will get <b><font color='#199C2C'>Satisfaction Points</font></b> that can be spent in the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Reward Store</font></b>."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Beginner\Beginner_Aspirations_3.png">2f7d0004:00000000:368df5a3db615173</T>
      <T n="text">0x48DF1A59<!--String: "Most <b><font color='#199C2C'>Aspirations</font></b> have multiple <b><font color='#199C2C'>Stages</font></b>, each with their own set of <b><font color='#199C2C'>Goals</font></b>. When all of them are completed, your Sim will get a powerful <b><font color='#199C2C'>Reward Trait</font></b>! \n\nYou can see your current Stage and the Reward Trait by hovering the cursor over the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Aspiration icon</font></b>. \n\nTo <b><font color='#199C2C'>change</font></b> your current Aspiration, use the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Select New Aspiration</font></b> button."--></T>
    </U>
  </L>
